document_data.name: Saklarra's Wonderful Willing Wenches
document_data.mainbody: '''Saklarra's Wonderful Willing Wenches''' was a brothel in [[Suzail]], [[Cormyr]], of the late 15{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.History: The place was [[Arclath Delcastle]]'s choice when he felt especially frisky around {{yearlink|1479}}.
